## Output Schema

### Eigenvector mode (default)

| Column | DuckDB Type | Description |
|--------|-------------|-------------|
| FID | VARCHAR | Family ID |
| IID | VARCHAR | Individual ID |
| PC1 | DOUBLE | First principal component score |
| PC2 | DOUBLE | Second principal component score |
| ... | DOUBLE | ... |
| PCn | DOUBLE | nth principal component score |

One row per sample.

### Eigenvalue mode (`output := 'eigenvalues'`)

| Column | DuckDB Type | Description |
|--------|-------------|-------------|
| PC | INTEGER | Principal component number (1-indexed) |
| EIGENVALUE | DOUBLE | Eigenvalue |
| VARIANCE_EXPLAINED | DOUBLE | Proportion of variance explained |
| CUMULATIVE_VARIANCE | DOUBLE | Cumulative proportion |

