## Risk Assessment

| Risk | Impact | Mitigation |
|------|--------|------------|
| NOLAPACK SVD too slow for > 5K samples | Performance | Phase 2 adds optional LAPACK |
| GRM memory for large N | OOM crash | Memory guard config option |
| Numerical precision vs plink2 | Test failures | Tolerance-based comparison |
| Randomized SVD implementation complexity | Scope creep | Defer to Phase 2 |

